          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The correction caused by difference in the source",
                " fission neutron spectrum and that of the Cf-252",
                " standard has been estimated using the experimentally",
                " confirmed efficiency versus neutron energy curve",
                " (see Boldeman, 2nd Nat.Soviet Conf. on Neutron Phys.,",
                " Kiev,May 1973,Vol.4 p.83) and assuming that the",
                " fission neutron spectra are accurately represented by",
                " a Maxwellian distribution with assumed temperature as",
                " the following:",
                "  kT=1.433+/-0.03 (Cf-252), 1.362+/-0.03 (Cm-248),",
                "     1.19+/-0.03 (Pu-240),  1.207+/-0.07 (Pu-242)."
              ]
            }
          ],
